## Clock
create_clock -period 41.667 -name sys_clk [get_ports clk]
set_property -dict {PACKAGE_PIN D13 IOSTANDARD LVCMOS33} [get_ports clk]


## User LEDs (L1-L8 shown; extend to L16)
